/w:LsdException>   <w:LsdException Locked=\"false\" Priority=\"32\" SemiHidden=\"false\"    UnhideWhenUsed=\"false\" QFormat=\"true\" Name=\"Intense Reference\"></w:LsdException>   <w:LsdException Locked=\"false\" Priority=\"33\" SemiHidden=\"false\"    UnhideWhenUsed=\"false\" QFormat=\"true\" Name=\"Book Title\"></w:LsdException>   <w:LsdException Locked=\"false\" Priority=\"37\" Name=\"Bibliography\"></w:LsdException>   <w:LsdException Locked=\"false\" Priority=\"39\" QFormat=\"true\" Name=\"TOC Heading\"></w:LsdException>  </w:LatentStyles> </xml><![endif]-->  <!--[if gte mso 10]> <style>  /* Style Definitions */ table.MsoNormalTable \t{mso-style-name:普通表格; \tmso-tstyle-rowband-size:0; \tmso-tstyle-colband-size:0; \tmso-style-noshow:yes; \tmso-style-priority:99; \tmso-style-parent:\"\"; \tmso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; \tmso-para-margin:0cm; \tmso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt; \tmso-pagination:widow-orphan; \tfont-size:12.0pt; \tfont-family:Cambria; \tmso-ascii-font-family:Cambria; \tmso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin; \tmso-hansi-font-family:Cambria; \tmso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin; \tmso-font-kerning:1.0pt;} </style> <![endif]-->    </p>\n<p>自 2011 年起，Graham Fink 就是奥美中国首席创意官，<a href=\"http://www.creativereview.co.uk/cr-blog/2016/february/graham-fink-photographs-a-changing-shanghai-in-riflemaker-exhibition/\">过去的五年里，他随手拍下了上海的飞速过渡和发展。</a>“上海的发展速度真是惊人” Fink 此前接受媒体采访时说，“旧建筑不断倒下，新建筑快速地拔地而起。在这样的环境里，你像是在经历世代的进化和推移。”</p>\n<p>世界对中国飞速发展的评论已经够多了，Graham Fink 说他的作品不想提供任何政治观，这些照片反而反映了一种远景，充满了浪漫和凄美。</p>\n<p>“我总是很着迷于死亡和重生的想法，”他说道，“一个城市也不例外。虽然破坏这个词充满了消极情绪，当你真的停下来，看看还剩下什么时，会在废墟中看到难以置信的美丽。孩子们绘制在墙上的画被孤零零地留了下来，人们的扶手椅被抛弃，它被重新遗留给自然。”</p>\n<p>“当你在废墟中穿行的时候，能闻到废弃建筑物独有的气味。它让你有轻微的威胁感和兴奋感，促使你去寻找那些被遗留下来的东西。”</p>\n<p>目前“上海民谣”（Ballads of Shanghai）展正在<a href=\"riflemaker.org\">伦敦的 Riflemaker gallery</a> 举行，将持续到 2 月 14 日。如果你在伦敦，可以在现场看到这些照片了。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150249pU28C7mM0VrjkieN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150250FzxaPdKA9vlRfe4k.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150250vHMPOnyF1VzQd7rE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150252I3ZnWQejx5wJCfTV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150252yzjsT4FVSxXNheoA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150253kTSuybFK952PmiND.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n \r\n  0\r\n  0\r\n  1\r\n  24\r\n  137\r\n  凤凰网\r\n  1\r\n  1\r\n  160\r\n  14.0\r\n \r\n \r\n  <o:AllowPNG></o:AllowPNG>\r\n \r\n</xml><![endif]-->\r\n\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:TrackMoves></w:TrackMoves>\r\n  <w:TrackFormatting></w:TrackFormatting>\r\n  <w:PunctuationKerning></w:PunctuationKerning>\r\n  <w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>10 pt</w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>\r\n  <w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>0</w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>2</w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas></w:ValidateAgainstSchemas>\r\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n  <w:DoNotPromoteQF></w:DoNotPromoteQF>\r\n  <w:LidThemeOther